{
  "id": "adv_card_kor_10_03",
  "title": "fran",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_greenscreen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "見て下さい。これがカカアコ名物のウォールアートです\nこれを見るとデザインのアイデアがわくんですよね！",
      "startTime": 5.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_greenscreen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 10.2661449115
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "ストリートアートでしか得られない感動もあって……\nここでお洒落して歩くのも凄く楽しいんですよ！",
      "startTime": 14.3666667938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（スタジオに到着するなり、撮影を始めたけど……）\n（カカアコってどこのことだ……？　ハワイ、だよな？）",
      "startTime": 21.8333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_evening",
      "startTime": 26.8391642571
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……さすがに妄想で演技するのは疲れるわね……\nもう限界……。いい絵、撮れました……？",
      "startTime": 34.7666680654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "や、やれることはやりましたよ……\n後はグリーンバックの部分に合成するだけですね……",
      "startTime": 43.6666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "合成……た、託しても、いいですか……？\n私、帰ってもまだブランドの仕事が残ってて……",
      "startTime": 54.5666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "はい、今日中……二十四時までには。franさんも\n出来れば休んで下さいね、明日はMV撮影がありますし",
      "startTime": 64.6000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "はい……何から何まで今日はありがとうございました\n{user}さん、後は、任せました……",
      "startTime": 76.1146707721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "―― 一月四日、MV撮影現場",
      "startTime": 82.3413120908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.802287102
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.974642881
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "動画の件、おかげ様でなんとか間に合いました\n時間がなかったので、もらった動画をそのまま送ったら",
      "startTime": 88.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.9054139776
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "「へー、家でゴロゴロしてて忘れてると思ってた」\nとかkanaに言われて、腹は立ちましたけど",
      "startTime": 96.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ゴロゴロというより、倒れてましたけどね……\nというか、結局日付をまたいでしまいすみません",
      "startTime": 102.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.6255956335
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "いいんですよ。さっき聞きましたけど、二人とも\nまだ送った動画見てませんでしたし。まぁ私もだけど",
      "startTime": 110.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.076819897
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "正直、昨日のこと自体よく覚えてませんけど、なんとか\nなりましたから。ふふ、じゃあ撮影いってきますね！",
      "startTime": 119.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.9333347321
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "この衣装だったら、こういう動きの方が映えますよね\nせっかくですし、もっと海外ウケするようにしますね",
      "startTime": 130.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "あ、サビの部分もう少しカメラ寄れますか？\n袖で一瞬レンズ隠して\n笑顔でアップにするのはどうです？",
      "startTime": 140.1333312988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（不安なんて全く抱いていなかったが、完璧以上だな……）\n（満身創痍のはずなのに現場を引っ張っている……）",
      "startTime": 147.2999959309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（ひとまず肩の荷が下りたようだし、出来る限り）\n（この後はゆっくり休んで下さいね、franさん……）",
      "startTime": 154.3333292643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――後日",
      "startTime": 158.7979029022,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 159.937713623
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ、年末年始の仕事もようやく落ち着いてきた\nん……kanaさんからメッセが来てるな",
      "startTime": 166.3666625976,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5935.4253448999825,
          "startTime": 166.7666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4302.08794249998,
          "startTime": 165.1333292643
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "「山田さんってば、ギャグ路線でいきたいらしいよ\n変な動画になったけど、本人の希望なんでよろしくー」",
      "startTime": 173.8999959309,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12733.337402399997,
          "startTime": 186.6333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ギャグ……？　この前撮った正月動画のことか？\nあれは確か、今日アップ予定のはずだけど……",
      "startTime": 183.6333292643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！\n動画！！　早く動画見て下さい！！",
      "startTime": 188.6710978256,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 185.33077210000215,
          "startTime": 187.4999959309
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 192.1992145858
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 192.1992145858
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、波の音が心地いいわね～！\nこの水着も持って来て良かった～！",
      "startTime": 197.9333435058,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 201.2425498011
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "あ、さっき話したポキ屋さんがありますよー！\nここのアボカドと新鮮なマグロの相性は抜群なんです！",
      "startTime": 204.9666788737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 210.4333455403
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "なっ、ハワイじゃなく京都になってる！？　海どころか\nタクシー乗り場でfranさんが水着ではしゃいでるぞ",
      "startTime": 215.566688029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "ポキ屋さんどころか、茶葉売り場の前なんですけど！\n動画作り終わった後、確認しなかったんですか！？",
      "startTime": 222.76668396,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "すみません！　編集でミスしたようです……\n確認不足でした……な、なんとお詫びすれば……",
      "startTime": 228.7000050862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "いえ……お互い限界なのは、承知の上だったので……\nというか、そのまま使ったkanaが一番悪いので",
      "startTime": 238.5666717529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "普通は変だと思ったら、確認したり止めますからね\nきっと面白がってわざと……。これ大丈夫でしょうか",
      "startTime": 246.6649733946,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_prowrestlingring-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s6",
      "startTime": 252.0333424886
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_prowrestlingring-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s6",
      "startTime": 252.0333424886
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
